{
  "texts": [
    "Therefore, it is recommended to start with a limited number of features before gradually adding more features based on needs.",
    "At each step, it is important to evaluate the accuracy of the predictive model.",
    "This will help to ensure that the predictions are accurate within a suitable number of features.",
    "Figure 15 shows the percentage of using each category of features in the reviewed studies.",
    "Among the findings, the student behavioral/activity features (click-streams) had the highest percentage of recurrence with 34%, followed by academic performance features with 32%, then demographic features with 30%."
  ]
}